"title": "5822: criticism, against believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5822: criticism, against believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Many notable servants of God were subject to criticism, which was sometimes vicious and severe. This was particularly true of Jesus Christ, who was constantly subject to complaint and criticism.</p>\n<h2>Examples of criticism directed against believers</h2>\n<h3>The patriarchs criticised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:25-Gen31:30\">GEN 31:25–31:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:17-Gen12:20\">GEN 12:17–12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:5\">GEN 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:9-Gen20:10\">GEN 20:9–20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:1-Gen30:2\">GEN 30:1–30:2</a></p>\n<h3>Moses criticised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:3\">EXO 17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:11-Exod2:14\">EXO 2:11–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:19-Exod5:21\">EXO 5:19–5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:11-Exod14:12\">EXO 14:11–14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:24\">EXO 15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:2\">EXO 16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:1-Num12:2\">NUM 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:1-Num16:3\">NUM 16:1–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:12-Num16:14\">NUM 16:12–16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:41\">NUM 16:41</a></p>\n<h3>David criticised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:28\">1SA 17:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:16-2Sam6:23\">2SA 6:16–6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:1-2Sam15:4\">2SA 15:1–15:4</a></p>\n<h3>Job criticised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:1-Job8:2\">JOB 8:1–8:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:1-Job11:6\">JOB 11:1–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:1-Job15:6\">JOB 15:1–15:6</a></p>\n<h3>The prophets criticised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:8\">JER 20:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:17\">1KI 18:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:24-1Kgs22:27\">1KI 22:24–22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:10-Amos7:12\">AMO 7:10–7:12</a></p>\n<h2>Criticism directed against Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ criticised by his family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:20-Mark3:21\">MRK 3:20–3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:48\">LUK 2:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:2-John7:5\">JHN 7:2–7:5</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ criticised by his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38\">MRK 4:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21-Matt16:23\">MAT 16:21–16:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31-Mark8:33\">MRK 8:31–8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:40\">LUK 10:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:60-John6:61\">JHN 6:60–6:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:6-John13:9\">JHN 13:6–13:9</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ criticised by the Pharisees</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:11\">MAT 9:10–9:11</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15-Mark2:16\">MRK 2:15–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29-Luke5:30\">LUK 5:29–5:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:1-Matt12:2\">MAT 12:1–12:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:23-Mark2:24\">MRK 2:23–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:1-Luke6:2\">LUK 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:1-Luke15:2\">LUK 15:1–15:2</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ criticised for his teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:41-John6:42\">JHN 6:41–6:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:3\">MAT 9:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:6-Mark2:7\">MRK 2:6–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:21\">LUK 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:52-John8:53\">JHN 8:52–8:53</a></p>\n<h2>Paul criticised</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:27-Acts21:28\">ACT 21:27–21:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12-Acts18:13\">ACT 18:12–18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:10\">2CO 10:10</a></p>",
